&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with various design tasks, such as developing layouts, templates, resizing or cropping images, retouching, compressing, or converting files across multiple software programs (web/mobile/print).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with various teams to interpret and transform raw data into clear and compelling charts, graphs, icons, graphics and other visual representations to convey information in an easily digestible format&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate to gather necessary information, clarify design requirements, and deliver effective solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure designs align with client branding guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform thorough quality assurance assessments on designs to guarantee accuracy, consistency, and compliance with brand guidelines before final delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Address client feedback professionally and make necessary revisions to address requested changes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple design projects simultaneously, adhering to deadlines and prioritizing tasks effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage design file organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
